      "id": "welcome_p1_en",
      "label": { "en": "[Section 1] Paragraph 1 (English)" },
      "default": "If this is your first time here — welcome. You've landed on the home of Palmetto Studios, a creative studio that uses fashion as its medium."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "welcome_p2_en",
      "label": { "en": "[Section 1] Paragraph 2 (English)" },
      "default": "What you'll find on the site: the current catalog of essentials, a lookbook, and the studio's ongoing work. New collections drop episodically rather than seasonally — each one a new world rather than a new wardrobe — so the site changes shape over time. What's here today won't be what's here next time."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "welcome_p3_en",
      "label": { "en": "[Section 1] Paragraph 3 (English)" },
      "default": "If you want the deeper context, the About page covers what the studio is and how it works. Otherwise, take your time, and feel free to write to us if anything catches your eye."
