      "label": { "en": "[Section 3] Paragraph 1 (English)" },
      "default": "The Palmetto Tree is usually a low-growing, fan-leaved palm. The reason for choosing this as a brand name is because it represents the little kid inside of us designing, creating, and innovating through this lens. I aim to introduce playful elements, nostalgia, and a bit of satire in my design ethos, striving to create products that spark a reaction and a sense of belonging."
    },
